➜磨耳朵夏天的英语童谣
http://www.sohu.com/a/411439033_100171577	11452
<p>炎热的夏天,小朋友们少不了属于夏天的歌谣，这个夏天一起唱起来~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Summer Songs</strong></p>
<p>这首歌节奏明快，听着听着身体都会不自觉地跟着晃动！朗朗上口的歌词，简单的句型，易发音的词汇，非常适合3岁以上的孩子哼哼唱唱哦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">What do you like to do in the summer?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你在夏天喜欢做什么呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">What do you like to do in the summer?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你在夏天喜欢做什么呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">I like to swim.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我喜欢游泳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">I like to bike.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我喜欢骑自行车.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">I like to surf.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我喜欢冲浪.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">I like to hike.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我喜换徒步旅行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">What do you like to do in the summer?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你在夏天喜欢做什么呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">What do you like to do in the summer?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你在夏天喜欢做什么呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">I like to read.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我喜欢阅读。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">I like to camp.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我喜欢露营。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">I like to play.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我喜欢玩。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
