<p class="ql-align-center">I like to dance.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我喜欢跳舞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">What do you like to do in the summer?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你在夏天喜欢做什么呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">What do you like to do in the summer?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你在夏天喜欢做什么呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">swim,bike.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">游泳，骑自行车。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">surf,hike.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冲浪，徒步旅行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">read,camp.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阅读，露营。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">play,dance.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玩，跳舞。</p>
